{"tid":320480,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無打工巴絲試過俾上司既說話呃左","createTime":"2017-07-13T14:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T14:47:18.000Z","uid":44725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2cbeeac9a6aa49c1878559e9ae7ceffe5477a2a8","tid":320480,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:20:33.000Z","msg":"你地有咩感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558b4ef6e478111254297eb0ec51127e53a41fc6","tid":320480,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:31:48.000Z","msg":"各為其主姐, 上司如果係manager grade, 就會為公司諗先"},{"pid":"b814640d458290aa0a88fa5a1519581e924fb0fe","tid":320480,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各為其主姐, 上司如果係manager grade, 就會為公司諗先</blockquote><br />\n我個上司係manager, 得我跟佢做野, 但點解佢要講說話呃我<br />\n<br />\n好唔開心試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cd3f798c4585495f2348e182cbae9b109e7210","tid":320480,"uid":107660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"同你講OT有補水，實際係乜春都冇 on99幫佢OT <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e694d2fa4bd97ad7a51d18ccd226b056206b5ebe","tid":320480,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:53:57.000Z","msg":"其實上司用說話呃下屬係咪好常見? (當佢想你唔好走個時)<br />\n<br />\n明明下屬係幫上司做野, 點解上司要用說話呃下屬? <br />\n<br />\n當知道左呃人既時候個感覺唔係更加差咩?"},{"pid":"f9cfb1a6cf4a83835801a6bba9f7ffd94fbe89bb","tid":320480,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"要學識分真假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口頭承諾一律當吹水<br />\n最緊要白紙黑字寫低"},{"pid":"a7544c9af3eb8e3574e67e614d22f5160bbd8116","tid":320480,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:59:21.000Z","msg":"成日架啦 講過唔算數，上司都係。一味吹水"},{"pid":"97b718aef91ebe7363f0126532c2013df893601b","tid":320480,"uid":53409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676e6dffb0c0e3a1c7674df13c84279b72241516","tid":320480,"uid":44725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要學識分真假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口頭承諾一律當吹水<br />\n最緊要白紙黑字寫低</blockquote><br />\n上司話想升我職, 前前後後講左三次, 上年12月做appraisal個時話要睇我表現, 下年應該會有得升職<br />\n<br />\n佢見我有D失望咁, 同我講話想升職既話可以同大老細提出, 其實佢係想玩我多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e51a296f4fa3452de0b67d9f742d3214e91a10","tid":320480,"uid":44725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要學識分真假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口頭承諾一律當吹水<br />\n最緊要白紙黑字寫低</blockquote><br />\n上司話想升我職, 前前後後講左三次, 上年12月做appraisal個時話要睇我表現, 下年應該會有得升職<br />\n<br />\n佢見我有D失望咁, 同我講話想升職既話可以同大老細提出, 其實佢係<span style=\"color: red;\">咪</span>想玩我多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"169eff59a7df957a9eef93fc628ed082af9991e3","tid":320480,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日架啦 講過唔算數，上司都係。一味吹水</blockquote><br />\n當我知道上司之前講左好多說話呃我, 而我仲要對住佢日日幫佢做野<br />\n<br />\n個種心情唔知有無人明白, 我果時坐係office位日日想自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e160f6c5a693a1153182f2bdb4fdffbedbef3097","tid":320480,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:11:39.000Z","msg":"係自己同大老細提出, 打少左"},{"pid":"9e673230d6871a581533263d261a65cccfac0960","tid":320480,"uid":103395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re